    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9dbaaaff09e000007a0f3",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/8ceacd73627793be67cc164d82ea53b7]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537858475,
      "updated": 1537858475
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9dbaaaff09e000007a0f2",
      "text": "[二語文]の生成",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537858474,
      "updated": 1595838780
    },
    {
      "id": "5f1e9131aff09e0000519444",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1595838770,
      "updated": 1595838770
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9db99aff09e0000cbebb6",
      "text": "ポステルの原則: [送信は厳密に、受信は寛容に]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537858457,
      "updated": 1537858493
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9dbc4aff09e0000cbebb8",
      "text": "\t受信と送信が同じモデルである必要はない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537858501,
      "updated": 1537858509
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9dbccaff09e0000cbebb9",
      "text": " [生身の人間]が発する言葉を受信する際には、寛容に、バリエーション豊かな表現を受理できる必要がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537858509,
      "updated": 1662606991
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9dbecaff09e0000cbebba",
      "text": " 一方で、自分が発信する際には、厳密な表現を行う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537858540,
      "updated": 1537858585
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9dc19aff09e0000cbebbb",
      "text": " \tつまり天然の[言語]の部分集合で構わない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537858585,
      "updated": 1537858966
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9dd97aff09e0000cbebbc",
      "text": " 単語を並べることはKJ法で付箋を近くに置くことに似ている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537858968,
      "updated": 1537858990
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9de47aff09e0000cbebbd",
      "text": " \tなぜ置いたかは言語的に説明できなくても良い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537859144,
      "updated": 1537859153
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9de50aff09e0000cbebbe",
      "text": " 発話意図",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537859153,
      "updated": 1537859182
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9de6eaff09e0000cbebbf",
      "text": " \t子供の発達過程を考えると、要望を伝えたり、事実を伝達したり",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537859182,
      "updated": 1537859197
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9de7daff09e0000cbebc0",
      "text": "  だけどボットに求められるのは[新結合創造]ではないか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537859198,
      "updated": 1595840329
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9de92aff09e0000cbebc1",
      "text": "  新結合創造の実装例はScrapboxの[2-hop link]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537859219,
      "updated": 1537859242
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9deabaff09e0000cbebc2",
      "text": "  \tキーフレーズの共起関係をたどって2つ先のページを表示する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537859244,
      "updated": 1537859446
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9df7eaff09e0000cbebc3",
      "text": " 近すぎるリンクは当たり前、遠すぎるリンクは意味不明",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537859454,
      "updated": 1537859481
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9df99aff09e0000cbebc4",
      "text": " \t程よいリンクが価値を生み出す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537859481,
      "updated": 1537859489
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9dfa0aff09e0000cbebc5",
      "text": "  cf. [カオスの縁] [弱いつながりと希少性]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537859489,
      "updated": 1537859513
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9dfe3aff09e0000cbebc6",
      "text": " ボットの発話モデル",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537859555,
      "updated": 1537859560
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9dfe8aff09e0000cbebc7",
      "text": " \t刺激に対して、誰かの言葉を再現する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537859560,
      "updated": 1537859569
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9dff0aff09e0000cbebc8",
      "text": "  1〜2単語を返す",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537859569,
      "updated": 1537859576
    },
    {
      "id": "5ba9dff7aff09e0000cbebc9",
      "text": "  問いかけを返す see: [クリーンランゲージ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537859576,
      "updated": 1537859591
    },
